message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with medical image analysis, specifically liver lesion segmentation in CT scans, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and medical imaging (cs.MED). The use of deep learning models and loss functions for segmentation also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
